1
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:14,680
Thank you, Papa Yin,

2
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,640
for being the first to like this video.

3
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,370
Follow me so you don't get lost.

4
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,160
Mr. Li,

5
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:30,250
what should we call the owner of this account?

6
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:33,920
My students told me to call them uploaders.

7
00:01:34,080 --> 00:01:35,880
Mr. Zhang told me they're called

8
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:36,800
bloggers.

9
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:39,009
Aren't they called streamers?

10
00:01:39,479 --> 00:01:41,400
Things on the internet change every day.

11
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:42,960
I really don't understand it.

12
00:01:42,960 --> 00:01:43,920
Tell me about it.

13
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,850
A couple of days ago,

14
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:47,560
my students told me,

15
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,160
Let's go. Let's head out.

16
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,440
I was left entirely speechless.

17
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,400
Mr. Yin,

18
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:56,860
what made you think of surfing the internet?

19
00:01:57,600 --> 00:02:00,060
Just trying to keep up with the young people.

20
00:02:14,720 --> 00:02:15,360
Ren Zhen.

21
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,860
How's it going?

22
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,720
I've uploaded four videos.

23
00:02:19,920 --> 00:02:21,040
I'm editing another one.

24
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:23,360
The completion rate is okay,

25
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:25,290
but the views aren't great.

26
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,360
The number of likes and comments

27
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,480
is less than forty.

28
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,440
It's okay. Take your time.

29
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:30,520
Do you still need to

30
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:32,200
shoot new footage today?

31
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,760
County leaders are coming for an inspection these days,

32
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:37,640
and I have some work to report.

33
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:38,480
How about

34
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:40,120
I ask Wulan to go with you?

35
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:40,800
No need.

36
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:42,600
I'm very familiar with the village now.

37
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,520
Yesterday, Grandpa Bate

38
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,360
even invited me over for goat milk.

39
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,090
Don't worry.

40
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,400
I'll look around by myself.

41
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,880
Okay, be safe.

42
00:02:49,440 --> 00:02:49,960
I'm off.

43
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:50,680
Bye.

44
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:48,000
Click here.

45
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,720
This little red heart, right? Yes.

46
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:51,320
Okay. You can only like a video once.

47
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:53,380
But you can leave multiple comments.

48
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:55,880
You can also send emojis in comments. Look.

49
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:57,480
This kitten is very popular.

50
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,360
This is a kitten. Send it again, sir.

51
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,960
Sir, you clicked the wrong one.

52
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:03,490
Sir, you clicked the wrong one. It's this one.

53
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,940
Goji berries, a gift from nature.

54
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:08,520
Ren Zhen.

55
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,920
How is your account doing?

56
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:13,880
Come on.

57
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:16,680
Fierce as a tiger,

58
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,200
only 250 likes

59
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,360
when looking back.

60
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,820
I see you already have a lot of loyal viewers.

61
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,880
And in the comment section,

62
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:26,480
you can bump into a few acquaintances and chat.

63
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,440
Dad Yin.

64
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,400
I find that your internet surfing

65
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:32,060
is getting better and better.

66
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,280
Those memes of yours are so funny.

67
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,960
I won't post memes anymore.

68
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,159
Why?

69
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:41,760
I found that netizens love using memes too much.

70
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:44,530
Replacing accuracy with inaccuracy.

71
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,320
If this goes on,

72
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:48,850
they will get further away from words.

73
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:51,000
It's easy to lose the ability to express oneself

74
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,320
in a real context.

75
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:54,800
True.

76
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,480
Young people nowadays

77
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,560
basically forget how to write once they pick up a pen.

78
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:01,220
And forget what they saw after watching a video.

79
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,520
Ren Zhen.

80
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,680
I feel you are a bit tense.

81
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,160
Here,

82
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,570
don't be afraid to express your feelings.

83
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,400
I...

84
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,200
I just hope

85
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,060
the account can grow quickly.

86
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,400
I hope everyone in Xia Village

87
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:25,120
can be happy.

88
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:33,960
Leave a comment and discuss with everyone.

89
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:34,159
Discuss together.

90
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:36,560
Leave a comment and discuss with everyone.

91
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,060
Three million.

92
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:40,920
101,000, 12,000.

93
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,040
52,000.

94
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:44,080
The account is taking off.

95
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,240
Look, look.

96
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,080
The account is taking off.

97
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:47,840
Let me see.

98
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:50,200
Wow! He's so handsome. This is not a TV drama.

99
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,560
Oh my, so handsome.

100
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,330
A boyfriend working in the system.

101
00:05:57,400 --> 00:05:58,530
What does this mean?

102
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,440
Oh my God.

103
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,760
It actually went viral this way.

104
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:10,460
Stop chatting.

105
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,130
Food is ready. Come and eat.

106
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,080
Look at this.

107
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:15,960
What's wrong?

108
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,840
Where is Xiacun?

109
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:22,640
A village cadre?

110
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:25,200
I want to be the goji berry in the cup.

111
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,120
Goji berries?

112
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,200
Our goji berries are getting noticed.

113
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,400
That's great. My god.

114
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:31,080
Let me see.

115
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:34,560
Why did the followers increase so much suddenly?

116
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,290
I took a video of Wulan singing,

117
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,840
and you were drinking water in the background.

118
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,040
The video went viral.

119
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,680
It's that simple?

120
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,680
Just that simple.

121
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,440
Sit down.

122
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,600
Our hero, sit.

123
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:45,960
I'm so happy.

124
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,280
If I had known this,

125
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,720
I would have ordered a batch of glasses.

126
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,840
Whoever appears on camera later

127
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,680
could hold a glass

128
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:53,210
and drink wolfberry water.

129
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:57,760
You were bad at describing pictures since childhood,

130
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,720
and you still haven't improved.

131
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:00,840
Sir,

132
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:03,020
why would you say that all of a sudden?

133
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,200
Even Yin's dad knows

134
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:06,120
why these netizens left comments.

135
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:06,980
Mr. Secretary,

136
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:09,160
take a closer look.

137
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:16,920
Th-They are looking at me!

138
00:07:19,760 --> 00:07:20,520
Zhenzhen.

139
00:07:20,960 --> 00:07:22,800
Is this what you always call

140
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:23,760
a viral point?

141
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,000
Exactly.

142
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,760
To keep making viral hits,

143
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:29,400
we need to keep catering to their tastes.

144
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,480
No, no.

145
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,040
I am the Party Secretary.

146
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,120
My job should be

147
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:35,200
to lead the village in development.

148
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,840
I can't be on camera doing a personal show.

149
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:39,640
If being on camera can promote Xia Village,

150
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:40,440
will you do it?

151
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,320
No.

152
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:45,170
Isn't that putting the cart before the horse?

153
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,960
I shot these videos

154
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:48,159
just to test the waters.

155
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:49,600
Whatever the netizens like,

156
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,600
the villagers' daily lives, or Xia Village's scenery.

157
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,680
No matter what we shoot,

158
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,600
the element of goji berries

159
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,840
must always be there.

160
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:56,960
This is called a subtle influence.

161
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:57,760
Now we finally have

162
00:07:57,760 --> 00:07:59,680
the viral moment everyone's been waiting for.

163
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,760
Jiao Li, you need to step up.

164
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:04,280
I think Zhenzhen has a point.

165
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:06,200
I've never seen the comment section

166
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,320
so lively.

167
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:10,320
No, stop forcing me.

168
00:08:10,440 --> 00:08:11,960
I don't know how to do this.

169
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,040
Don't worry.

170
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,120
I'm here.

171
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:18,440
Just focus on being your internet-famous party secretary.

172
00:08:18,440 --> 00:08:19,970
What are you planning to do?

173
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,560
Drink water.

174
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,640
Water is what we're drinking.

175
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,440
Next, we'll

176
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,960
drink it up.

177
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:53,880
Stop.

178
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,640
Isn't it just drinking water?

179
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:57,120
Just drink it.

180
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:58,440
Renzhen,

181
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:01,440
how about letting Shuji go to the bathroom first?

182
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,570
He's already had six glasses of water.

183
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,540
What exactly do you want to shoot?

184
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:08,440
You guys really don't know what I want.

185
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:10,840
We don't know.

186
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:12,920
Watch.

187
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,240
I want your

188
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:17,800
slender fingers holding the cup.

189
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:21,000
Then bring it to your lips.

190
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,800
Now, take a small sip.

191
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:28,800
Let the goji berries slowly swirl up

192
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:30,560
and settle back to the bottom.

193
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:32,020
At this moment,

194
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,720
the goji berry water slides right down your throat.
